    Menschenrechte
  </h3> <div class="h-[32px]"></div> <p class="break-words font-400 text-light-gray text-[16px] leading-[24px] tracking-[0.15px] md:text-[20px] md:leading-[32px]">
    Wir glauben an Gleichheit und glauben das jeder fair, ungeachtet seines Geschlechts, seiner Religion oder einem anderen Faktor, behandelt werden sollte.
  </p> <div class="h-[40px] md:h-[48px]"></div></div></div><div><div class="flex flex-col text-center shadow-pricing-action-card rounded-[10px] border border-lavender px-[48px] md:px-[24px] h-full"><div class="h-[40px] min-h-[40px] md:h-[48px] md:min-h-[48px]"></div> <div class="mx-auto flex items-center justify-center min-h-[168px] h-[168px]"><picture><source media="(min-width: 768px)" type="image/webp" data-srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/0x168/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/235x150/530cd05f64/group-3915.png 1x, https://img2.storyblok.com/0x336/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/235x150/530cd05f64/group-3915.png 2x" srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/0x168/filters:format(webp):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/235x150/530cd05f64/group-3915.png, https://img2.storyblok.com/0x336/filters:format(webp):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/235x150/530cd05f64/group-3915.png 2x"> <source media="(min-width: 768px)" data-srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/0x168/filters:format(png):quality(75)/f/145847/235x150/530cd05f64/group-3915.png 1x, https://img2.storyblok.com/0x336/filters:format(png):quality(75)/f/145847/235x150/530cd05f64/group-3915.png 2x" srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/0x168/filters:format(png):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/235x150/530cd05f64/group-3915.png, https://img2.storyblok.com/0x336/filters:format(png):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/235x150/530cd05f64/group-3915.png 2x"> <source type="image/webp" data-srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/0x128/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/235x150/530cd05f64/group-3915.png 1x, https://img2.storyblok.com/0x256/filters:format(webp):quality(75)/f/145847/235x150/530cd05f64/group-3915.png 2x" srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/0x128/filters:format(webp):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/235x150/530cd05f64/group-3915.png, https://img2.storyblok.com/0x256/filters:format(webp):blur(30):quality(30)/f/145847/235x150/530cd05f64/group-3915.png 2x"> <source data-srcset="https://img2.storyblok.com/0x128/filters:format